my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-humanization.md:39:**Phase 3 — Memory, silence, ensemble (CCH-022..CCH-029).** R9 Motif memory with LRU + variation menu + return-home decay. R10 Silence budgets with wind-voice lung-capacity caps. R11 Call-response gating. Section-level envelope compositing. Tempo-dependent swing (Friberg/Sundström). Arc-shape variety. Restraint as global dampener. End-of-phase: 5-minute generative pieces no longer feel looped; repetition-variance metrics pass thresholds.
